{{Vgname|疯狂龙卷风|en=Tornado Mania!}}是[[Digital_Chocolate|Digital Chocolate]]开发的2005年[[手机游戏|手机游戏]]。玩家扮演一名科学家，他制造龙卷风收集建筑，建造自己的[[乌托邦|乌托邦]]。

== 玩法 ==

玩家扮演一名对事件逐渐厌倦的科学家，他决定建立自己的孤立乌托邦<ref name="modojo">{{cite web|url = http://www.modojo.com/reviews/mobile/tornado_mania/20071128/585/|title = Tornado Mania Review|author = Davis, Justin|publisher = Modojo|date = 2007-11-28|accessdate = 2008-10-21|archive-date = 2007-12-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071217072448/http://www.modojo.com/reviews/mobile/tornado_mania/20071128/585/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。游戏的“乌托邦模式”结合了《[[块魂|块魂]]》和《[[模拟城市|模拟城市]]》的元素，龙卷风会将建筑移动到指定位置，合适的位置会提升乌托邦居民的幸福值<ref name="pocket gamer review">{{cite web|url = http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Mobile/Tornado+Mania/review.asp?c=2059|title = Mobile Game Review - Tornado Mania|author = Dredge, Stuart|publisher = Pocket Gamer|date = 2006-12-25|accessdate = 2008-10-21|archive-date = 2008-10-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081002131224/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Mobile/Tornado+Mania/review.asp?c=2059|dead-url = no}}</ref>。玩家无法直接控制龙卷风路线；它会以顺时针弧线穿过陆地，玩家可以颠倒逆时针方向，指挥龙卷风移动<ref name="ign review">{{cite web|url = http://uk.wireless.ign.com/articles/750/750258p1.html|title = Tornado Mania Review|author = Buchanan, Levi|publisher = [[IGN|IGN]]|date = 2006-12-08|accessdate = 2008-10-21|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081230090537/http://uk.wireless.ign.com/articles/750/750258p1.html|archivedate = 2008-12-30}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==

游戏获得游戏媒体的积极评价，包括IGN的10/10分<ref name="ign review">{{cite web|url = http://uk.wireless.ign.com/articles/750/750258p1.html|title = Tornado Mania Review|author = Buchanan, Levi|publisher = [[IGN|IGN]]|date = 2006-12-08|accessdate = 2008-10-21|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081230090537/http://uk.wireless.ign.com/articles/750/750258p1.html|archivedate = 2008-12-30}}</ref>，以及IGN的2006年12月月度游戏奖<ref>{{cite web|url = http://uk.wireless.ign.com/articles/761/761286p1.html|title = Game of the Month: December 2006|author = Buchanan, Levi|publisher = [[IGN|IGN]]|date = 2006-12-31|accessdate = 2008-10-21|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110713005100/http://uk.wireless.ign.com/articles/761/761286p1.html|archivedate = 2011-07-13}}</ref>。

